PREECE
CHARDONNAY, 1997
The complex and elegant Precce Chardonnay is made from grapes grown
in the premium wine-making region of Victoria
The 1997 vintage offers sweet fruit flarours, augmented by spiey
orertones and well-balanced acidity. A delightful wine to drink at any
time. with seafood or seier dishes.
MITCHELTON
GOULBURN VALLEY SHIRAZ 1996
Australia's Goelburn Valley has been producing Shiraz of remarkable
depth and flavour for more than 130 years, a tradition that continues
with Mitchelton Goulburn Valler Shiraz.
The hallmarks of this wine are intense fruit flarours and a rounded,
mouth filling texture. The wine is matured in oak barrels for 16 months
and blended with small amounts of Grenache and Mourredre to add
further earthiness and spice. The 1996 vintoge offers a warm, mulbern
fruit aroma with a velvety well-balanced palate - the perfect
accompaniment to beel or lamb

for drinking shortly after bottling
